item.description: Let's hike up to Cole Pond for a day of swimming, exploring, and lunch. There is a rope swing into the water. The more adventurous can also hike to Butternut Pond (compass and map skills would come in handy for this - unless someone in the group knows where to go). We could have a pot luck lunch and grill some hamburgers or hot dogs.

group.name: Lebanon/White River Junction Hiking Meetup Group

item.name: Day at Cole Pond
